rows.label: tev040301_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Oche about recent developments.

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0001
rows.name:
Most Prone histories were destroyed in war with
Cavern Clan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0002
rows.name:
Now storytellers like Nimu Turton must pass on legacy
of Prone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0003
rows.name: Would you know our past? Then speak to Nimu.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0004
rows.name: He is wise. Kind. Wonderful. Go speak with him![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0010
rows.name:
Earth alien came to me recently. He was angry.
Said I killed his friends.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0011
rows.name:
This made me realize truth.
Cavern Clan did terrible things to Earth aliens.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0012
rows.name:
I am Tree Clan. Not Cavern Clan. Yet I will not hide
from Earth-alien anger.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0013
rows.name:
Cavern Clan used cowardly tactics.
Killed many of my Tree Clan friends.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0014
rows.name:
So I understand your Earth-alien pain.
Perhaps more than anyone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0020
rows.name:
Nimu has spoken. He demands that Prone keep new
history of Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0021
rows.name:
I tried to use Earth-alien device called
"viddy ocammara." It was not successful.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0022
rows.name:
Ocammara was difficult to use. Also flimsy.
I accidentally crushed it with feeblest of blows.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0023
rows.name:
You need stronger machines, Earth alien.
Build ocammara like Prone weapon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0030
rows.name:
Ma-non machines listen to Prone. Do as they are told.
Very easy to use.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0031
rows.name: But sometimes wrong machine hears command.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0032
rows.name:
Once I bellowed for single door to open.
Ended up opening every door on ship.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0033
rows.name:
Ma-non say to "keep voice down." But I cannot.
Prone are not good at being kept down![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0038
rows.name:
Nimu deserves to be heard across whole city.
Just like your Chausson![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0039
rows.name: Nimu deserves to be on teller vision![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0040
rows.name:
We Prone must work hard. Learn to use your
"viddy ocammara" machines.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0041
rows.name:
Handling delicate equipment is hard.
Much harder than slaying giant beast.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG0042
rows.name:
But one day we will succeed.
I will be first Prone ocammara operator ever![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG1001
rows.name: Slovity is too strong. I lose every duel![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG1002
rows.name: I must win. Or Mira will think Tree Clan weak.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG1003
rows.name:
I must train with weapons and viddy ocammara.
But there isn't time![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG1004
rows.name: Grrr! War is over! Why so many things to do?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040301_MSG3001
rows.name:
We have no chance against horde that big.
Please help us.[ST:wait ]
